#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"Block editor toolbar addition for mixed Rtl Ltr writing directions. Wrap "
"words (or sentences) in paragraph block with span element and change their "
"direction from rtl to ltr and vice versa. Uses dir=\"rtl\" or dir=\"ltr\" "
"See also https://www.w3.org/International/articles/inline-bidi-markup/. <br> "
"Note that the wrapping element is <span dir=\"rtl\" || dir=\"ltr\" "
"class=\"atr-inline-direction-rtl\" || class=\"atr-inline-direction-ltr\"> so "
"you can control it through your site CSS as well. I.E. .atr-inline-direction-"
"rtl{direction: rtl;display:inline-block}"
msgstr ""
"התוסף מוסיף כפתור לסרגל הכלים של עורך הבלוקים שמטרתו להקל על עריכת טקסטים "
"בכיוונים מעורבים Rtl Ltr. הוא עוטף מילים (או משפטים) בפסקה בבלוק ברכיב span "
"ומשנה את הכיוון שלהם."

